Plastic allows you to check if credit card numbers were entered correctly.

Example:

var Card = new Plastic('4111-1111-1111-1111');

Card.isValid();
//True

Card.type();
//visa

Card.number();
//removes spaces and alpha characters
//4111111111111111

Card.isLuhnMatch();
//Could be used to display custom error messages
//True

Plastic does not depend on any JavaScript frameworks
You can modify the cc object to add support for more credit card types

Plastic is not a substitude for server side validation!